---
name: Custom Checkboxes and Radio Buttons
description: These are available with special code that needs to be precicely used.
order: 1
notes: |
    - use `mzp-c-input-choice` for both checkboxes and radio buttons
    - the input must be before the label in source order
---

<form class="mzp-c-form">
  <fieldset class="mzp-c-form-set">
    <legend class="mzp-c-form-label">Choices <span class="mzp-c-fieldnote">(in this case checkboxes)</span></legend>
    <div class="mzp-c-choices">
      {{#embed "patterns.molecules.forms.fields.choice" id="s-check-1" type="checkbox"}}{{#content "label"}}Option 1{{/content}}{{/embed}}
      {{#embed "patterns.molecules.forms.fields.choice" id="s-check-2" type="checkbox"}}{{#content "label"}}Option 2{{/content}}{{/embed}}
    </div>
    <p class="mzp-c-form-info">With more information about these choices.</p>
  </fieldset>

  <fieldset class="mzp-c-form-set">
    <legend class="mzp-c-form-label">Inline Choices <span class="mzp-c-fieldnote">(in this case radio buttons)</span></legend>
    <div class="mzp-c-choices mzp-l-choices-inline">
      {{#embed "patterns.molecules.forms.fields.choice" id="sic-1" type="radio" name="sic"}}{{#content "label"}}Option 1{{/content}}{{/embed}}
      {{#embed "patterns.molecules.forms.fields.choice" id="sic-2" type="radio" name="sic"}}{{#content "label"}}Option 2{{/content}}{{/embed}}
      {{#embed "patterns.molecules.forms.fields.choice" id="sic-3" type="radio" name="sic"}}{{#content "label"}}Option 3{{/content}}{{/embed}}
    </div>
    <p class="mzp-c-form-info">With more information about these choices.</p>
  </fieldset>

  {{#embed "patterns.molecules.forms.fields.choice" id="s-terms" type="checkbox"}}{{#content "label"}}Single checkbox <span class="mzp-c-fieldnote">With a fieldnote</span>{{/content}}{{/embed}}

  {{#embed "patterns.molecules.forms.fields.choice" id="s-terms2" type="checkbox" is-legal="true"}}{{#content "label"}}Single checkbox with less prominent label{{/content}}{{/embed}}
</form>
